name: Eternal Essence
description:
We had the most beautiful skies this year, full of vibrancy and dramatic light and clouds. The reduction in travel has meant less pollution in the sky and a greater clarity.

This painting was created during the time I had the virus. I didn't know I had it. My symptoms were slight but included a change of visual perspective. I feel the beauty of that state is in this little painting. An awareness of minute details and bright colours.
